{"word":"ὑπερίσχω","slug":"ὑπερίσχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερίσχω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ὑπερέχω'><el>ὑπερέχω</el></a>, <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be above, to prevail over</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to protect</i>, <el>τινός</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}